{"tid":1931242,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"外流港將徐宏傑隊友感染武漢肺炎 全隊剛從泰國集訓返回中國正進行隔離","createTime":"2020-03-18T05:23:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-02T04:17:13.000Z","uid":9030,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"2f78729cde95e0080bed84371775045e429fdf72","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:23:36.000Z","msg":"【梅州隊前鋒多利確診新冠肺炎】3月17日0時至24時，廣州市報告新冠肺炎新增確診病例3例，均為輸入病例，其中包括中甲球隊梅州客家的巴西外援前鋒多利。據梅州隊員透露，由於早已發燒，多利在下飛機之後就立即被帶走了。據悉，與多利相關的 42 名密切接觸者尚未出現症狀，梅州隊的其他球員、教練和工作人員暫時都還沒事，但處於隔離狀態。"},{"pid":"6d73a687fe740371ff1592546426905b68fe96fe","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:36:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2tLP4z6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2tLP4z6.png&h=12363c6b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d681fdcca1acc66e9fa5050e0d8b10bd0d4f0b36","tid":1931242,"uid":318069,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:42:39.000Z","msg":"傑仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n咁努力青年軍後備到一隊<br />\n點知撞到武肺"},{"pid":"63ef7a98ef70befcc956c29d4b05d3a784ecd7ed","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:48:31.000Z","msg":"2月3-3月16日，中甲梅州客家隊在泰國進行聯賽備戰訓練<br />\n<br />\n3月16日，患者從泰國曼谷乘坐9C6316航班途經廣州白雲國際機場入境，經海關排查後轉運至廣州市胸科醫院隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\n3月17日，市疾控中心檢測患者新冠病毒核酸陽性，即轉至廣州市第八人民醫院隔離治療。<br />\n<br />\n3月17日晚，經專家會診，診斷為新冠肺炎確診病例。<br />\n<br />\n3月17日，初步甄別42名密切接觸者均在梅州集中隔離醫學觀察。"},{"pid":"76edbd15a5a094b773e8f2b61a2da143619048fd","tid":1931242,"uid":174432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:09:50.000Z","msg":"唔怪得入境嗰陣搞咁耐"},{"pid":"84a2af6c0317c83d28cbb199ccbe63bb6b2434b6","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:09:56.000Z","msg":"徐宏傑回應查詢時指球隊正進行隔離，而自己亦已為新冠肺炎進行第一次測試，結果呈陰性。不過他稱：「早幾日才跟他一起食飯，全日都與他在一起，所以還要驗多幾次才清楚。」"},{"pid":"d11b55e5a28e9112d83c95a68a9f30e0695e5ded","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:10:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n早幾日才跟他一起食飯，全日都與他在一起"},{"pid":"ca11e8b0812445ee6905531c9c1f9815675291e7","tid":1931242,"uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:13:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hOXt2dSTfyA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhOXt2dSTfyA&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=c5eced86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hOXt2dSTfyA</a>"},{"pid":"06c632ede08a52e8a944b8b915aa9434574636bd","tid":1931242,"uid":7439,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:15:31.000Z","msg":"支那人：快啲死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://n.sinaimg.cn/sports/transform/671/w432h239/20191218/2d81-ikvenfu0212569.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fn.sinaimg.cn%2Fsports%2Ftransform%2F671%2Fw432h239%2F20191218%2F2d81-ikvenfu0212569.gif&h=79c1c526&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"233b06a30ee9c17ab112fe5a491c2486973ddc6d","tid":1931242,"uid":60658,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:23:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8f6237cc90f3d