" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"695d481dbd79caba568c9d55d635192b6805154a","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00f5c08cc6687b41a69dfacfbe9531d367860940","tid":1931242,"uid":117802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:41:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:00:54.000Z","msg":"慘, 其實好高危, 3日前成日同dori一齊"},{"pid":"1ac208304260b807c4a6af6cd4fef81a82baec55","tid":1931242,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:11:40.000Z","msg":"咁都有得反<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9a4e7fc9df497f62411acbd0b3e2fb6d208eca8","tid":1931242,"uid":133687,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b6cbd3d4b1da89839755deb077d268cc0b957ec","tid":1931242,"uid":205377,"like":2,"dislike":21,"score":-19,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:38:42.000Z","msg":"個樣有陣支那味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:13:20.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"42f3a68496c5278498f28e9ff5dce946d9cf69b4","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca11e8b0812445ee6905531c9c1f9815675291e7","tid":1931242,"uid":7439,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T06:13:18.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hOXt2dSTfyA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DhOXt2dSTfyA&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqFwUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=c5eced86\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hOXt2dSTfyA</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:26:36.000Z","msg":"經典"},{"pid":"baa3653da7e048323c66b258c95da8746d79b812","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T07:41:42.000Z","msg":"因國外疫情嚴重，梅州客家臨時決定16日中午全隊乘機回國，全隊在當日下午4點平安抵達白雲國際機場。在抵達機場後，全隊按照國外旅客入境廣東相關流程進行健康監測。據了解，在機場全隊共約耗了6個小時才得到相關工作人員允許放行，回到五華已是凌晨。在機場健康監測時，其中巴西外援多利被篩查出來，疑似感染新型冠狀病毒，隨後立即被轉運至廣州市胸科醫院進行隔離觀察，昨天，經廣州市疾控中心檢測，多利的新冠病毒核酸呈陽性，初步確診他感染新冠病毒肺炎，即轉至廣州市第八人民醫院隔離治療，3-5天后將復查確認。<br />\n據了解，在這兩周泰國華欣集訓期，進行了一場熱身賽，賽后原地放假了一天。至於多利是在哪感染的仍需要確認。<br />\n隊內其他隊員包括工作人員回到梅州五華後，昨天在足球小鎮集中隔離，今天全隊已到相關定點集中隔離醫學觀察，目前全隊並無異常！"},{"pid":"06b24fe75776fdbd5dbada7d7e91d641ff4c2828","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"徐宏傑證實梅州客家的職球員需在當地政府安排的隔離所接受隔離，他表示自己跟球會並無特別措施防疫，只聽從隔離所的安排：「我哋每日都有檢疫測試，要量體溫，<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋隔離所會畀啲中藥我哋飲</span>。」"},{"pid":"d6204d6b36786bd1c53c0cad1557f8b75377a9fe","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T09:51:04.000Z","msg":"徐宏傑表示，原留在球隊公寓隔離，但昨早證實有隊友確診，市政府隨即要求球隊到隔離營"},{"pid":"a80678517fff5588016a064c4190317c16265f31","tid":1931242,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"06b24fe75776fdbd5dbada7d7e91d641ff4c2828","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"徐宏傑證實梅州客家的職球員需在當地政府安排的隔離所接受隔離，他表示自己跟球會並無特別措施防疫，只聽從隔離所的安排：「我哋每日都有檢疫測試，要量體溫，<span style=\"color: red;\">同埋隔離所會畀啲中藥我哋飲</span>。」"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T10:07:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f265fdb37d927e556220f7943af5aeccb69e26a8","tid":1931242,"uid":9030,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"a80678517fff5588016a064c4190317c16265f31","tid":1931242,"uid":62073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"